## BT solution

From frist glance, this issue can be easy solved by BT , the steps can be :
- start from lan 2, keep moving until see the block in lan 2
- once facing block,  we have 2 choices, jumping to the next 2 lans
- start the same process, until reach the end

code  (timeout for some test case):
