Thanks to the suggestion by @anindya-saha; Here is a very elegant Solution. The solution works great in these questions: 
* [295. Find Median from Data Stream](https://leetcode.com/problems/find-median-from-data-stream/discuss/1246287/Java-clean-O(logN)-TreeSet-Solution-oror-with-comments)
* [1825. Finding MK Average](https://leetcode.com/problems/finding-mk-average/discuss/1222887/Java-Elegant-O(log-M)-add-O(1)-avg-TreeSet-Solution)
